title: Mr Boukadoum receives his Malian counterpart
text: The Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr. Sabri Boukadoum, received on Sunday, his Malian counterpart, Mr. Zeyni Moulaye, who is on a working visit to Algiers at the head of a high-level ministerial delegation to participate in the 16th session of the Algerian-Malian bilateral strategic committee.

The session, which will be co-chaired by the two ministers, will focus on the examination of several files relating to bilateral and regional relations, in addition to measures likely to accelerate the pace of the implementation of the Peace and Reconciliation Agreement, emerged from the Algiers process.
